{"tid":1779310,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"大家諗下䵝解瑞典環保少女會贏左香港示威者？","createTime":"2019-12-11T14:41:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-12T02:43:14.000Z","uid":149978,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"329a4a067e25c66d6c6e2e7e47c24a862cd75e17","tid":1779310,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T14:41:32.000Z","msg":"我估：有政府或政治勢力向 TIMES 施壓，TIMES低頭<br />\n<br />\n所以結果TIMES俾左個政治角力比較最細的瑞典環保少女。"},{"pid":"3f3574656c6f2451776270e6bb74f4ba6d4ad2b9","tid":1779310,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T14:42:10.000Z","msg":"努力打好國際線<br />\n今日香港都成為美加焦點<br />\n<br />\n 【Twitter要人!!】美加議員人權日tweet集合list!!!!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1779138\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1779138</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">需要人入去推post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">Twitter 需要大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"6049619aed049d45aa291bac5a131dec7a8d00f5","tid":1779310,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T14:45:34.000Z","msg":"另外係環保撚在英國倫敦搞左個反滅絕示威<br />\n不合作/勇武程度都唔少野<br />\n同佔中有得fight<br />\n搞到英國交通大癱瘓<br />\n<br />\n瑞典少女環保鬥士通貝里（Greta Thunberg）周日在倫敦聲援抗議氣候變化的示威者，呼籲他們永遠不要放棄拯救地球的行動。與此同時，當地警方因示威群眾在倫敦市各地標造成交通大亂，已拘捕900多人。<br />\n<br />\n16歲的通貝里在大理石拱門（Marble Arch）告訴歡呼的群眾：「我們是帶來改變的人，我們是『反抗滅絕』（Extinction Rebellion）和『為氣候罷課』（School Strike for the Climate）的孩子，我們是作出改變的人。」<br />\n<br />\n她說：「我們永遠不會停止戰鬥，我們永遠不會停止為地球、為自己、為我們及子子孫孫的未來奮鬥。」<br />\n<br />\n通貝里去年8月帶著「為氣候罷課」的標語，站在瑞典首都斯德哥爾摩國會前為環保請命，引發多國兒童、青少年跟進，展開抗議全球暖化的運動。<br />\n大理石拱門是過去7天因抗議活動而陷入癱瘓的多個倫敦地標之一。警方已因這波抗議潮逮捕963人，當中42人被控。<br />\n<br />\n「反抗滅絕」抗議活動主辦單位表示，英國政府若願討論他們的訴求，他們願意在本周將抗議策略從干擾改為對話，否則會把抗議行動升級。「反抗滅絕」是學術界人士去年在英國成立的團體，是全球崛起速度最快的環保運動之一。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/984755/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B-%E7%91%9E%E5%85%B8%E7%92%B0%E4%BF%9D%E5%B0%91%E5%A5%B3%E8%81%B2%E6%8F%B4%E5%80%AB%E6%95%A6%E6%B0%A3%E5%80%99%E8%AE%8A%E5%8C%96%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85-%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E5%9B%A0%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%E5%A4%A7%E4%BA%82%E6%8B%98%E9%80%BE900%E4%BA%BA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F984755%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B-%25E7%2591%259E%25E5%2585%25B8%25E7%2592%25B0%25E4%25BF%259D%25E5%25B0%2591%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E8%2581%25B2%25E6%258F%25B4%25E5%2580%25AB%25E6%2595%25A6%25E6%25B0%25A3%25E5%2580%2599%25E8%25AE%258A%25E5%258C%2596%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A8%2581%25E8%2580%2585-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%2596%25B9%25E5%259B%25A0%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E9%2580%259A%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E4%25BA%2582%25E6%258B%2598%25E9%2580%25BE900%25E4%25BA%25BA&d=WPWOQTheSiAT%2FB2p9vAnAKC2H8C9v%2BSdTXBEGJsevNE%3D&h=13705a4e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F984755%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B-%25E7%2591%259E%25E5%2585%25B8%25E7%2592%25B0%25E4%25BF%259D%25E5%25B0%2591%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E8%2581%25B2%25E6%258F%25B4%25E5%2580%25AB%25E6%2595%25A6%25E6%25B0%25A3%25E5%2580%2599%25E8%25AE%258A%25E5%258C%2596%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A8%2581%25E8%2580%2585-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%2596%25B9%25E5%259B%25A0%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E9%2580%259A%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E4%25BA%2582%25E6%258B%2598%25E9%2580%25BE900%25E4%25BA%25BA&h=493b4f1a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/984755/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B-%E7%91%9E%E5%85%B8%E7%92%B0%E4%BF%9D%E5%B0%91%E5%A5%B3%E8%81%B2%E6%8F%B4%E5%80%AB%E6%95%A6%E6%B0%A3%E5%80%99%E8%AE%8A%E5%8C%96%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85-%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E5%9B%A0%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%E5%A4%A7%E4%BA%82%E6%8B%98%E9%80%BE900%E4%BA%BA</a>"},{"pid":"b78eb9267bef0b5c547921c1425bfe51bb5b3eea","tid":1779310,"uid":316308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T02:43:14.000Z","msg":"瑞典環保HI，要求全球都用清潔能源，DLLM非洲同胞無銀瑞典會幫助佢地咩！就好似當年英國10嵗小學鷄寫信俾馬來西亞總理話人地砍伐樹木係不道德，因爲佢要研究熱帶樹木！真係好L笑"}]}